    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Montgomery</placeName>
                <date>Decb. 6 “48</date>
            </p>
            <p>The Chefra Mef. Cholim</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">to <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee> “
                    <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">We send you<lb/> enclosed Three Dollars for the Occident from<lb/>
                last year, and you will please direct<lb/> the Same the next time to</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <persName role="author">Mrss J &amp; G Myer</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <placeName>Montgy. Ala</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>About our Chefra we have to write you,<lb/> that she is going on very well, we
                have<lb/> now <add>בית הקברות</add>
                <add>“Beit Hakvachot” JE transliteration</add>, and have rented<lb/> a Synagogue,
                also the Election of<lb/> our Officers took place on the <date>5th of<lb/> November
                    48</date>. and it is elected</p>
            <list type="ordered">
                <head/>
                <item n="1"><persName>Jacob Myer</persName> President</item>
                <item n="2"><persName>P. Krans</persName>, Vice president</item>
                <item n="3"><persName>Emanuel Lehman</persName>, Secretary</item>
                <item n="4"><persName>Henry Weil</persName>, Treasurer</item>
                <item n="5"><persName>M. Englander</persName>, Trustee</item>
                <item n="6"><persName>Charles Levy</persName>, <add>?</add></item>
            </list>
            <p>Please inset this in your next Occident,<lb/> and write me please an
                    <sic>answere</sic>, &amp;<lb/> by so doing we are respectf.</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">The President</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">
                <persName role="author">J Myer</persName>
                <persName>Em. Lehman</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)">Secret:</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(7)"><placeName>Pa</placeName>|</p>
            <p rend="Note:">“Hevra Mevaker Holim” written in right margin; #001 6.6.94 circled and
                [?] Judaica Alabama [?] written in left margin</p>
        </body>
